{"tid":1911801,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣讚男人靚","createTime":"2020-03-05T14:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T17:08:42.000Z","uid":336090,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d09959cba5c645b70a560ba3f4e73b65e3667e11","tid":1911801,"uid":336090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T14:59:42.000Z","msg":"男朋友好鐘意人讚佢靚仔<br />\n可能因為佢天秤座太自戀<br />\n<br />\n我成日都好想讚佢靚仔<br />\n但讚嚟讚去都係靚仔<br />\n唔同讚女人咁多詞彙<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">想問下大家有咩讚男人嘅詞彙</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家會話女人皮膚靚咗<br />\n但話男人皮膚靚咗又好似好怪<br />\n會話女人個日套衫好靚<br />\n但男人根本都唔襯衫<br />\n會話女人髮質好咗<br />\n但男人短頭髮根本睇唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇Ching 幫到我"},{"pid":"5a176ca1cee4077e3d7c1018a4de4abbbc4f2c17","tid":1911801,"uid":167904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:00:45.000Z","msg":"條J好Cute <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b442cbbe69200f8abca0db8f4dd727a9523ed3b","tid":1911801,"uid":226466,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:01:02.000Z","msg":"你下面都幾強壯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c078ca04e2a4c0bffe994cd0212a2f55ac78b82","tid":1911801,"uid":156064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:01:28.000Z","msg":"讚佢柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2939b1d89f174644bba1f767dc2becae8c4b924","tid":1911801,"uid":20924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"型英帥靚正<br />\n梅花間竹咁撈亂嚟用啦"},{"pid":"280c4a56d19237b853e175c542edf8c7e90ff4fe","tid":1911801,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T1